name: 美少女万華鏡－神が造りたもうた少女たち－ 亜璃子 / Bishoujo Mangekyou－Kami ga Tsukuritamouta Shoujo－Alice / 美少女万华镜－神所创造的少女们－亚璃子
description:
2023,04,21 v2.0

三个衣服能正常画出来了，第四个那个红色的大礼服画不好，不知道写什么描述词能辅助AI画出来

泳衣：Alice-sw, swimsuit

护士：Alice-nu, nurse

女仆：Alice-en, enmaided, black thighhighs

私服：Alice-pc, (我不知道怎么写能画出来，辅助不明白，就当他没有吧)

Google Translate:

The three clothes can be drawn normally, The fourth red dress is not well drawn. I don’t know what descriptors to write to help AI draw it.

Swimsuit: Alice-sw, swimsuit

Nurse: Alice-nu, nurse

Maid: Alice-en, enmaided

Private Clothes：Alice-pc, (Think of prompt words yourself, this is not easy to draw)

OLD v1.0

默认动作叉腰（气急败坏）。三件衣服：女仆，泳装，护士。

护士服装忘了修改tag文本了，直接是AI自己检测的，写bikini就行，还是能凑合画出来的。

Google Translate:

The default action is akimbo. Three clothes: maid, swimsuit, nurse.

I forgot to modify the tag text for the nurse’s costume. It is directly detected by the AI itself. Just write bikini, and it can still be drawn barely.
